      "title": "Army cultivates 500 acres of maize",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Army has commenced cultivation of 500 acres of maize in the first phase today (27) at the Niraviya Army Farm in Thambuththegama covering an area of \u200b\u200b100 acres.",
        "Maj. Gen. Jagath Kodithuwakku, Chief of Staff of the Sri Lanka Army and several members of the Army were also present at the occasion."
      ],
